            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OPPO 近日在世界流动通讯大会（Mobile World Congress，MWC）发布全新「辅助实境智能眼镜」OPPO Air Glass 3 概念产品，据官方资料显示，OPPO Air Glass 3 能够利用手机专属 App 使用 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3，图片来源：OPPO</p><p>OPPO 表示，Air Glass 3 XR 现阶段属概念产品，重量仅在 50g 左右，采用 OPPO 自主研发的树脂晶圆衍射光波导镜片，折射率高达 1.70，显示亮度均匀性大于 50%，入眼峰值亮度超过 1000 尼特。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221791" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO 示范影片可见， Air Glass 3 XR 能显示不少资讯</p><p>OPPO 官方表示，使用者可利用手机里的 OPPO Air Glass 3 专属应用程式，开启旗下自主研发的 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 专属应用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲轻触眼镜的镜臂就能够使用语音助理功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 XR 实际佩戴</p><p style="text-align: left;">虽然 OPPO 这款 XR 眼镜看起来非常高科技，而且官方示范影片里面出现的功能亦很实用，OPPO 方面尚未透露 Air Glass 3 XR 上市时间表，因此就让我们拭目以待吧。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51149"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SedimxtA73g?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: left;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.oppo.com/cn/newsroom/press/514/">OPPO</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SedimxtA73g">Oppo@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/06/oppo-find-n3-flip-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】OPPO Find N3 Flip　外形　手感　铰位　功能　屏幕　相机　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/nokia-and-oppo-sign-crosslicense-5g-patent-agreement/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OPPO 与 Nokia 签订专利交叉授权，终止长达两年诉讼战</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/">【MWC 2024】OPPO Air Glass 3 智能眼镜加入 AI「AndesGPT」    戴眼镜开会即总结会议要点</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
